      <h2 class="white">Jumpstart Your Genealogy</h2>
      <h5 class="white">Chicago Family History Fair 2015</h5>
      <p class="white">Saturday, March 21st, 2015 â€” 8 am to 5 pm<br>2727 Lake Avenue, Wilmette, Illinois</p>

      <p class="smaller-text white">Are you just getting started with genealogy research or are you looking to get back on track? Sign up to attend the 2015 Chicago Family History Fair! We're offereing a full day of helpful classes designed to help you make progress towards your genealogy goals.</p>

      <p class="smaller-text white">Our keynote speaker is <a href="http://hidefgen.com/about/thomas-macentee/">Thomas McEntee</a>, founder of <a href="http://www.geneabloggers.com">GeneaBloggers.com</a> and a genealogy educator of renown. Thomas will present four of his most popular and engaging workshops:</p>

