      <%= link_to "Register Now (It's Free!)", new_registrant_path, class: "button round alert small-12 large-12 medium-12 columns" %>

    </div>
  </div>

<div class="full-width-container three">
<div class="row extended-vertical-padding">
  <div class="small-4 medium-4 large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag "workshops.jpg", class: "image-centered" %>
    <h4 class="text-centered">Presentations</h4>
    <p class="smaller-text">Couldn't make it to Salt lake City for RootsTech 2015? Come get the same great genealogy content here at teh Chicago Family History Fair. We'll offer some of the best talks from RootsTech on vido in three parallel tracks. We'll have great live presentations from local genealogists.</p>
    <div class="text-centered"><%= link_to "Schedule Highlights", schedule_path %></div> 
  </div>

  <div class="small-4 medium-4 large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag "exhibits.jpg", class: "image-centered" %>
    <h4 class="text-centered">Exhibits</h4>
    <p class="smaller-text">Chicago has lots of local organizations that can help you fill in the branches of your family tree. Check out the booths in the exhibit hall to get to know local historical and cultural societies. You'll also be able to sample family recipes handed down through generations, and even try your hand at indexing.</p>
    <div class="text-centered"><%= link_to "List of Exhibitors", exhibits_path %></div> 
  </div>

  <div class="small-4 medium-4 large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag "expert_help.jpg", class: "image-centered" %>
    <h4 class="text-centered">Expert Help</h4>
    <p class="smaller-text">Looking for one-on-one help finding answers to your family history questions? Visit our family History Center and sign up for a personal consultation with one of our experienced genealogical researchers. Or get friendly assistance translating Polish, German, or Japanese records. The cost? Free, of course.</p>
